{{multiple issues| {{NPOV language|date=September 2010}} {{notability|Events|date=June 2014}} {{update|date=April 2016}} }} {{Infobox music festival | name =Cali Underground | image =Cali Underground 18 julio 08 288.jpg | caption = | location = | years_active = | founders = | dates = | genre = [[Rock music]] | attendance = | capacity = | website = }}
'''Cali Underground''' is an annual rock music festival celebrated in [[Cali]], [[Colombia]]. Bands as [[Angelcorpus]], [[Ultimos Romanticos]], Astreas Domains, Desdenia, Deadline and Orus have played at this festival.
== History ==
The first running of this festival was in 2004 with the presence of only a few hundred visitors before a few relatively unknown bands, but at the following year the number of visitors increased to several thousands. After obtaining the support of the [http://www.cali.gov.co/index.php?servicio=Noticias&funcion=ver&id=6674 Secretaria de Cultura y Turismo de Santiago de Cali] and private enterprises like [[Parquesoft]]<ref>[http://www.parquesoft.org/informacion/producto.php?seleccion=104 Parquesoft]</ref> and Deeplunar<ref>[http://www.deeplunar.org Deeplunar]</ref> the festival drew more visitors.
