{{unreferenced|date=September 2009}} The '''Norwegian Touring Car Championship''' (or '''NTCC''') was held for three seasons between 2002 and 2004. The series used cars from the [[British Touring Car Championship]] and the [[Deutsche Tourenwagen Masters]] (DTM) that were built between 1987 and 1995. The series became inactive when it merged with the Swedish SSK series in 2005.
